spm commands largely modelled after yum.
spm packages modelled on pacman/rpm
FORMULA files flexible - anyone host own repos
  spm will ignore fields it does not understand (for in-house implementation)

2015.8 minimum version

$ tree
some-formula/
  some/
    init.sls
    map.jinja
FORMULA
$ spm build some-formula/

